title: Red Dwarf - Complete Series High Quality
description:
I encoded these for my own use and have decided to share them

All the encodes i have come across on the net have been ass so i did them myself
Please seed nice as decent rips are non existent 

Series 1-8 the quality isnt that great to start with this is a good as it gets from the dvd's

Series 9 was filmed at 25fps and released on blu-ray 
framerate converted to 30fps VC-1 no idea what they where upto there..

Series 10 is fine its H264 25fps 

Series 1-8 encoded by myself from DVD9 images
Series 9 encoded by myself from the blu-ray
Series 10 Reumx'd by myself from the blu-ray

Settings used

Transmission 0.10.0.6534
Decomb = Default
Framerate = Constant 25fps
Rate = 2 Pass 2500 kbps
x264 Preset = Very Slow
x264 Tune = Film
H.264 Profile = High
H.264 Level = 4.1
Audio = Auto Passthru

Series 9
Video = CQ12, Framerate Same as source, Decomb, Very Slow, Level 4.1 High
Audio = Auto Passthru

Series 10
Video = Remux
Audio = DTS to AC3 640

feel free to post if i have made any file name mistakes etc..

Please share nice as this is 76gb
im not sharing out to every single person
